{"tid":785378,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"恆動派社區服務義教導師招募","createTime":"2018-08-19T07:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T02:14:30.000Z","uid":4273,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f72a51fd4a5b18d3bcca0e412a02bde63c2a5b3","tid":785378,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"恆動派社區服務 x (香港青年協會 及 社會福利署) 基層學生義教導師招募 <br />\n<br />\n香港縱然是個國際都市，貧富懸殊一直居於世界前列。低收入家庭礙於經濟問題，往往未能提供予其子女一個校外的學習支援。 <br />\n<br />\n有見及此，恆動派社區服務聯同香港青年協會以及香港社會福利署，於2018年籌劃不同的基層學生義教服務。目的改善學生校內成績，減輕校園生活所帶來的學習壓力。 <br />\n<br />\n香港青年協會及社會福利署，將扮演提供義教課室及學生的角色，而恆動派社區服務既為合作組織，故現正招募有意參與義教服務的導師，及統籌義教服務的幹事。 <br />\n<br />\n報名及詳情： <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2v03ZCp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v03ZCp&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=52e7a135\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2v03ZCp</a>"},{"pid":"13b552c8e2548bb4436ec13d5f50255aacd60a4d","tid":785378,"uid":4273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港青年協會 (已由2018年2月開始運作) </strong><br />\n義教地點：香港青年協會　賽馬會橫頭磡青年空間 (樂富地鐵站步行約5分鐘） <br />\n義教對象：黃大仙及樂富區，低收入家庭之小學生 <br />\n義教時間：星期三及星期六，每次時間約1.5小時 <br />\n義教形式：小班教學，以補習形式為主 <br />\n學生數目：每次約3-4名學生 <br />\n導師數目：每次為2-3名 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>社會福利署 (已由2018年5月開始運作) </strong><br />\n義教地點：社會福利署　北沙田綜合家庭服務中心 (沙田禾輋商場步行約5分鐘） <br />\n義教對象：沙田及大埔區，低收入家庭之小學生 <br />\n義教時間：星期六，每次時間約2小時 <br />\n義教形式：小班教學，以補習及遊戲形式為主 <br />\n學生數目：每次約7-8名學"},{"pid":"a766f929f2b65abaf9f25fa4510296fe7cf23a32","tid":785378,"uid":4273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"義工情報局 V.I.A<br />\n<br />\n一個每天都會收集及發放香港義工活動的頻道。因發現不少義工都沒有渠道去找義工活動，而有需要義工的機構或團體相對地宣傳度也不足夠，所以希望透過自己空餘的時間，幫手收集並發放義工資訊，讓大家多一個更容易接觸義務工作的機會。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp Channel：<br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/invite/60mUXp7hGm67DlCeuVSTgG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com%2Finvite%2F60mUXp7hGm67DlCeuVSTgG&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=bfe3a5a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/invite/60mUXp7hGm67DlCeuVSTgG</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram Channel：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/VolunteerIntelligenceAgency\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FVolunteerIntelligenceAgency&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=33da27cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/VolunteerIntelligenceAgency</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook Page：<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/VolunteerIntelligenceAgency\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2FVolunteerIntelligenceAgency&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=6ff41607\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/VolunteerIntelligenceAgency</a>"},{"pid":"d8b65718fcfc236d202acc25add1d4f826486fd1","tid":785378,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"點教佢地都係唔會成材架啦 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c2e827d60bd499aff299a20c2ce644abf42323","tid":785378,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/152431_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F152431_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b1b22dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賤人<br />\n已完"},{"pid":"136599bb8dc35e447bfcfcd6455c067b3bf9d599","tid":785378,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"勞力係應該well paid的<br />\n係資主主義先出現帶錢做野咁on9"},{"pid":"0bed8f26f104f8ebd6559a4287e50cc4bafb4da5","tid":785378,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c2e827d60bd499aff299a20c2ce644abf42323","tid":785378,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/201